com.hazelcast.client.proxy

Class IExecutorDelegatingFuture<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.client.util.ClientDelegatingFuture<V>
      • com.hazelcast.client.proxy.IExecutorDelegatingFuture<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - Type of returned object from the get method of this class.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompletableFuture<V>, InternalCompletableFuture<V>, Future<V>

    public final class IExecutorDelegatingFuture<V>
extends ClientDelegatingFuture<V>
    An Abstract DelegatingFuture that can cancel a Runnable/Callable that is executed by an IExecutorService. It does this by sending a Cancellation Request to the remote owning member and then cancelling the running task.
